# Customer — Profile Endpoints
# UC-006 (view profile), UC-021 (update profile)
# TenantContext populated from X-Tenant-ID / X-Actor-ID headers (set by BFF).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run seed
#   4. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### GET /customers/me — get authenticated customer profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/me
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{customerId}}
X-Actor-Type: CUSTOMER
X-Actor-Role: CUSTOMER
X-Correlation-ID: test-corr-id

###

### PATCH /customers/me — update customer profile (partial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/customers/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{customerId}}
X-Actor-Type: CUSTOMER
X-Actor-Role: CUSTOMER
X-Correlation-ID: test-corr-id

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "phone": "31999999999",
  "defaultAddress": {
    "street": "Av. Afonso Pena",
    "number": "1000",
    "complement": null,
    "neighborhood": "Centro",
    "city": "Belo Horizonte",
    "state": "MG",
    "zipCode": "30130921"
  }
}

###

### PATCH /customers/me — clear phone and defaultAddress
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/customers/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Actor-ID: {{customerId}}
X-Actor-Type: CUSTOMER
X-Actor-Role: CUSTOMER
X-Correlation-ID: test-corr-id

{
  "phone": null,
  "defaultAddress": null
}
